And for those who dont get the point of them, there are two things for eg, for me its usefull cuz my dvd-writer on my laptop is busted so if i need to write the iso i need to put it on my desktop, but i only have a 2gb pendrive so i just make into multiple volumes of 2gb and transfer it on my desktop.
for torrents its useful cuz, if a file gets corrupted in the downloading process u can just download that particular rar file again instead of downloading the entire 3 gb iso.
